data.enText: a natural substance found in food that is an essential part of what humans and animals eat to help them grow and stay healthy. There are many different vitamins .

data.chText: 增加了维生素的早餐谷物食品

simple_means.memory_skill: vit 生命 + am 获得 + in …素 → 生命要素 → 维生素

tr: any of a group of organic substances essential in small quantities to normal metabolism

value.def: Vitamins are substances that you need in order to remain healthy, which are found in food or can be eaten in the form of pills.

example.ex: Butter, margarine, and oily fish are all good sources of vitamin D.
example.tran: 黄油、人造黄油和多脂鱼都含有丰富的维生素D。

example.ex: Healthy people do not need vitamin supplements.
example.tran: 健康的人不需要额外补充维生素。

trans: 维生素C，抗坏血酸(存在于柑橘、柠檬等水果和绿色蔬菜)
